00:25:16.640 --> 00:25:17.480
Nagkamali ako.

00:25:18.090 --> 00:25:19.050
huwag kalimutan,

00:25:20.020 --> 00:25:21.390
Ako ang iyong kuya.

00:25:23.580 --> 00:25:24.450
Kuya?

00:26:08.140 --> 00:26:09.210
Su Muyang,

00:26:10.550 --> 00:26:11.880
